{"tid":82573,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"<求意見>繼續用大牛龜PC定細機+NAS？","createTime":"2017-01-16T05:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T14:49:11.000Z","uid":7782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88e966f05201fad3a6f45852c613f37e6fc3b0a1","tid":82573,"uid":7782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"話說我部舊機好似就嚟收皮，亦用左差唔多5年，所以計劃緊換機...<br />\n<br />\n舊機係大case，打機+BT組合，行緊4隻HDD，其中一pair係mirror!<br />\n<br />\n不過近幾年已經唔係點打機，唯獨係4隻HDD裡面嘅嘢要keep...<br />\n<br />\n所以考慮緊嚟緊繼續用大牛龜pc插晒4隻HDD落去好，定係買部文書廠機/mac mini 加隻NAS好？！<br />\n<br />\n想轉細機加NAS主要係想慳位同除塵方便d，如果繼續用大機就總係想砌好少少...<br />\n<br />\n請巴打比d意見，如果簡單4 bay NAS幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611c2ffa6d7b012145c0d251d2608dfaa58c0a73","tid":82573,"uid":19039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"你買nas之前搵定hdd做backup先<br />\n唔係煩到仆街都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37736df9928570f1b41329f6529723f9463d067b","tid":82573,"uid":7782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你買nas之前搵定hdd做backup先<br />\n唔係煩到仆街都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我重未決定一定轉NAS...不過已經諗過就算轉，都只係留番兩隻做mirror，又唔係要起RAID 5，所以應該搵多一隻HDD嚟過data就夠，問題不大..."},{"pid":"2525044208042a70d15fc0bb26240cc30fabad35","tid":82573,"uid":7782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:49:11.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}